::Autofire/Stratus::

Realizing that the bot he had brought in was no longer there, Autofire frowns and enters the base, walking around to find something interesting (orders).
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Stratus jumps up after being knocked down by Slaughter a long time ago. He fires two more pods and watches them crawl over the ground toward the crazy animal.
